Company Overview of eCurv, Inc.



Snapshot People




Company Overview
eCurv, Inc. develops Queued Power Access system, a cloud-based network system that delivers measurable reductions in peak demand charges for businesses. It governs the connection time of a range of electrical loads, including commercial HVAC systems, industrial refrigeration, electric heating, pumps, motors, battery charging stations for EVs, and industrial pumping. The company was founded in 2011 and is based in Cambridge, Massachusetts with an additional office in Newton, Massachusetts.


One Broadway14th FloorKendall SquareCambridge, MA 02142United StatesFounded in 2011



