Company Profile
Sector: Technology
Industry: Hardware
Sub-Industry: Electronics Components
eCurv, Inc. provides technology for commercial users of electricity to reduce their utility charges. The Company offers solution that enables businesses to integrate their building management systems and environmental equipment such as electric pumps, motors, battery charging stations, and refrigeration equipment. eCurv serves customers in the United States.




